docs.text: mermaid.initialize({ startOnLoad: true }); Welcome to MkDocs For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit. Project layout mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files. graph TD A[Start] --> B{Is it working?} B -- Yes --> C[Great!] B -- No --> D[Debug] D --> B Z@{ shape: manual-file, label: "File Handling"}
